1. Mi smo *povezani* kablovima. (We are *connected* by cables.)
2. Oni su *povezani* porodičnim vezama. (They are *connected* by family ties.)
3. Njih dvojica su *povezani* poslom. (The two of them are *connected* through work.)
4. Moramo biti *povezani* tokom ovog projekta. (We need to be *connected* during this project.)
5. Kablovi su *povezani* na zadnjoj strani računara. (The cables are *connected* to the back of the computer.)
6. Oni su *povezani* zajedničkim interesovanjima. (They are *connected* by common interests.)
7. *Povezani* smo u istoj mreži. (We are *connected* on the same network.)
8. *Povezani* ste sa osobom koju tražite. (You are *connected* with the person you are looking for.)
9. Ova dva grada su *povezana* auto-putem. (These two cities are *connected* by a highway.)
10. Ova knjiga je *povezana* s drugom knjigom. (This book is *connected* to another book.)